msgstr "批次元数据中的删除无效：只应包含已删除的行。"

#: src/git_stage_batch/batch/ownership.py:937
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Cannot select only part of this change.\n"
"Select all related lines together: {required_ids}\n"
